OL,3,CTV stars back campaign to raise final
OL,4,C#2.5 million for Royal Marines museum
OL,6,FTV personalities Ross Kemp and Dan
OL,7,FSnow have given their backing to help
OL,8,Fraise the final #2.5 million needed to
OL,9,Fcreate a new museum aimed at paying
OL,10,Ftribute to the "courage, sacrifice,
OL,11,Fand service" of the Royal Marines.
OL,13,FThe National Museum of the Royal Navy
OL,14,F(NMRN) is making the final push to
OL,15,Ffund the #15 million Royal Marines
OL,16,FExperience, which is being created at
OL,17,Fthe Portsmouth Historic Dockyard.
OL,26,@rD@POUsD@LO]
