CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774944309
OL,3,CTV stars back campaign to raise final
OL,4,C#2.5 million for Royal Marines museum
OL,6,FThe centre, which has been supported
OL,7,Fby a #4.4 million grant from The
OL,8,FNational Lottery Heritage Fund ` along
OL,9,Fwith funding from the Garfield Weston
OL,10,FFoundation, NMRN reserves and private
OL,11,Fdonations, is being designed as a
OL,12,Fplace of "remembrance and inspiration"
OL,13,Fwith interactive experiences to tell
OL,14,Fthe story of the elite force which was
OL,15,Fformed in 1664.
OL,26,@tD@JOUtD@fO]
