PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774944309
OL,3,CTV stars back campaign to raise final
OL,4,C#2.5 million for Royal Marines museum
OL,6,FActor and presenter Kemp, who reported
OL,7,Ffrom the front line in Afghanistan
OL,8,Fwhile he was embedded with British
OL,9,Fregiments including 45 Commando Royal
OL,10,FMarines, said: "I've been with Royal
OL,11,FMarines on the ground, and you see it
OL,12,Fup close, the discipline, the humour,
OL,13,Fthe calm under pressure, and the
OL,14,Ffierce loyalty to the person beside
OL,15,Fthem.
OL,17,F"The Royal Marines Experience matters
OL,18,Fbecause it captures that truth, not as
OL,19,Fmyth, but in the voices of the people
OL,20,Fwho lived it."
OL,26,@rD@POUyD@AOU|D@NO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
