PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774944309
OL,3,CTV stars back campaign to raise final
OL,4,C#2.5 million for Royal Marines museum
OL,6,FHistorian Dan Snow said: "The Royal
OL,7,FMarines are woven through over 360
OL,8,Fyears of British history, from the age
OL,9,Fof sail to the present day.
OL,11,F"What makes their story exceptional is
OL,12,Fnot just what happened, but the
OL,13,Fstandard behind it, and the people who
OL,14,Fcarried it.
OL,16,F"The Royal Marines Experience will
OL,17,Fsafeguard that living history and
OL,18,Fshare it with the public in a
OL,19,Fpowerful, modern way."
OL,26,@nD@ZOUsD@AOUxD@AOU{D@VO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
