CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774944309
OL,3,CTV stars back campaign to raise final
OL,4,C#2.5 million for Royal Marines museum
OL,6,FThe new centre will also include a
OL,7,F"Remembrance Room" where families can
OL,8,Freflect on those who have died while
OL,9,Fserving the country.
OL,11,FSarah Adkins, sister of the late Major
OL,12,FGeneral Matt Holmes ` a former head of
OL,13,Fthe Royal Marines, said: "Matt said
OL,14,F'Once in the Royal Marines family,
OL,15,Falways in the Royal Marines family'.
OL,17,F"The families of Royal Marines,
OL,18,Fserving and former, are very much part
OL,19,Fof the Corps family.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@RO]uD@ZOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
