PN,41806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774944309
OL,3,CTV stars back campaign to raise final
OL,4,C#2.5 million for Royal Marines museum
OL,6,F"The Remembrance Room will provide a
OL,7,Fspecial space in which to remember
OL,8,FRoyal Marines no longer with us,
OL,9,Fhonouring both their service and those
OL,10,Fwho grieve their loss.
OL,12,F"The pride in the Green Beret and all
OL,13,Fthat it stands for unites everyone in
OL,14,Fthe Royal Marines family, irrespective
OL,15,Fof connection, rank, length of
OL,16,Fservice, combat experience and age."
OL,18,FMatthew Sheldon, NMRN CEO, said: "Most
OL,19,Fof us will never know what it feels
OL,20,Flike to earn and wear the green beret
OL,21,Fof the Royal Marines Commandos.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@dO]zD@bOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
