FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774944309
OL,3,CTV stars back campaign to raise final
OL,4,C#2.5 million for Royal Marines museum
OL,6,F"So, we want our new Royal Marines
OL,7,FExperience to bring visitors closer to
OL,8,Fthe tests of their training and the
OL,9,Freality of their deployment, using
OL,10,Freal voices and remarkable objects.
OL,12,F"However, of course the Royal Marines'
OL,13,Fhistory stretches back across 360
OL,14,Fyears of service, so we have created a
OL,15,Fnew national home that connects this
OL,16,Flong tradition to the professionalism,
OL,17,Fcourage and pride of today's commandos.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
