PN,41808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774944309
OL,3,CTV stars back campaign to raise final
OL,4,C#2.5 million for Royal Marines museum
OL,6,F"We want every visitor to leave with a
OL,7,Fdeeper understanding of history, but
OL,8,Falso and especially of the challenges
OL,9,Ffaced by these men and women on behalf
OL,10,Fof the nation, in a period of such
OL,11,Fchange."
OL,13,FLieutenant General Sir Robert Fulton,
OL,14,Fa former commandant general Royal
OL,15,FMarines, said: "The Royal Marines
OL,16,FExperience is not just a building - it
OL,17,Fis a promise.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@HO]wD@POU
